Name: window_slider
Version: 0.8
Summary: A lib to implement sliding window with overlapping on numpy array
Home-page: https://github.com/imravishar/sliding_window
Author: Ravi Sharma
Author-email: ravi.sharma.cs11@gmail.com
License: Apache2
Description: A python package to run sliding window with overlapping on numpy array
        
